    "body": "This isn't a bug per se, but something I will think about. The issue is actually that `df[:4]` is a view on the original array, but the assignment\n\n```\ndf[:4]['B'] = range(4)\n```\n\nactually causes the `dtype` of the `B` column to change from floating point to integer. I think this is fixable but I need to decide what is the right behavior. \n"
